{"parents": [], "prev": null, "next": null, "title": "Play Recording Block", "meta": {}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"play-recording-block\">\n<h1>Play Recording Block<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#play-recording-block\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">The <strong>Play Recording</strong> block is only available when designing a workflow for a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/voice_campaigns.html\">voice campaign</a> or when managing a workflow for a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/phone/guides/numbers/phone_numbers.html\">phone number</a> .</div>\n<div class=\"line\">This block allows you to play a more personal experience for callers/recipients - who will hear a message from a pre-recorded human voice.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Place a <strong>Play Recording</strong> block in your workflow where desired</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Choose or record an audio file</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>You can either <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_upload_a_file.html\">upload</a> an existing audio file or record your own with one of the two options below</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/play_recording_microphone.html\">Microphone</a></p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/play_recording_phone_call.html\">Phone Call</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>In the workflow, you can now click <strong>show more</strong> and <strong>Play recording</strong> to hear your audio recording</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"]], "sourcename": "users/automation/guides/workflows/play_recording_block.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Play Recording Block</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/automation/guides/workflows/play_recording_block", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}